TEST STEPS

1. Open group context in a text editor;
2. Open the same context in a context editor;
3. Change tag in a text editor and save it;
4. Verify that tag was changed in context editor;
5. Repeat vice-versa: change tag in a context editor, verify it has been changed in a text editor.
